						               													<description>Summary:&amp;#10;This card games simulates a rugby match.&amp;#10;You attempt to move the ball down field to score before your opponent.&amp;#10;You can attempt to score in different ways depending on where you are on the field.&amp;#10;Cards let you move further down the field, stop ypur opponent, attempt a kick to score, attempt a try (like a touchdown), etc.&amp;#10;There is also a variable ending to each half of the game.&amp;#10;Powerful cards that are discarded can then be picked up, so you must weigh their use.&amp;#10;Lots of room for strategy and tactics, despite the deceptively simple game play.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Text on back of box:&amp;#10;&amp;quot;It doesn't matter if you actually play Union or even if you know the rules or not... Rugby Mania is VERY SIMPLE to learn, but provides hours of FUN&amp;quot;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;quot;Clear the decks, deal the cards and prepare for battle..... Are you brave enough to handle the action?&amp;quot;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;quot;A level playing field for men, women and children? A game that really is fun for adults and kids?&amp;quot;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;quot;If you are looking for the ultimate holiday game, or simply to tear the fmily away from the tv, or to have some mates over and end up scrimmaging all over the living room floor, THIS IS IT!&amp;quot;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;WARNING This game is addictive  - and can be played almost anywhere&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Proudly made in Australia&amp;#10;Ages 8+&amp;#10;2-8 Players&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
